 Validation of Saliva in the Esoterix Genetic Laboratories Fragile X Assay@highlight

The purpose of this research is to determine if saliva samples can be used as an alternate sample type to test for fragile X.

 By using saliva instead of blood, it would be easier for patients to have fragile X testing.

